snippet.textDisplay: In today’s internet where we see a lot of manufactured beauty (makeup, surgery, injections, extreme posing, lighting, editing, heavy retouching...) Cristine is so refreshing to look at, she’s such a natural beauty :). In fact, she’s exceptionally gorgeous, despite having almost no resemblance to the cookie-cutter “beauty” we see everywhere else online these days. Kids, take note! I know you see it too, I know no one is surprised when I say Cristine is beautiful. Does she have lip injections? Nope. Does she have big fake boobs and a bbl? Nope. Do we all need that to be beautiful? Hell no!!!! Embrace what makes you different and own the hell out of it, we don’t all need to be the same :)
